latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A tribute to the maestro @official.yiruma . Made this edit back in 2016. Initially the plan was to make a track with rap vocals featuring @earthgrime , but then plans changed, and then lost the project file in a hard disk crash. Had an export, fortunately. Released it, cause why not?
